The workspace is in an **extremely healthy, submission-ready state**. All core milestones (**M0–M8**) are fully integrated, and local validation gates pass successfully. Gitleaks scan reports **zero secrets in the git history**, and the golden demo runner consistently passes its validation asserts five out of five times. The OpenAI integration is syntactically correct against the installed `openai` Python SDK (v2.36.0) Responses API contract. 

There are no severe UI bugs or major gaps. We have identified minor documentation discrepancies and cleanup recommendations that can be resolved locally tonight, separated from external blockers.

